name: KMXMLParser
tagline: XML Parser for iOS. Get data from an RSS feed in 2 lines of code.
body: KMXMLParser is a simple class you can add to your iOS project to make parsing any standard RSS feed simple. Just drag the class into your project, add a couple of lines of code, and the RSS feed will be returned in an array which allows you to easily access the main elements of the RSS feed.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
